#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:328
msgid "Enumerations"
msgstr "枚举"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:338
msgid "enum **FocusMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **FocusMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:340
msgid ""
"**FOCUS_NONE** = **0** --- The node cannot grab focus. Use with "
":ref:`focus_mode <class_Control_property_focus_mode>`."
msgstr ""
"**FOCUS_NONE** = **0** —— 该节点无法获取焦点。与 :ref:`focus_mode "
"<class_Control_property_focus_mode>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:342
msgid ""
"**FOCUS_CLICK** = **1** --- The node can only grab focus on mouse clicks."
" Use with :ref:`focus_mode <class_Control_property_focus_mode>`."
msgstr ""
"**FOCUS_CLICK** = **1** —— 该节点只能获取鼠标点击的焦点。与 :ref:`focus_mode "
"<class_Control_property_focus_mode>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:344
msgid ""
"**FOCUS_ALL** = **2** --- The node can grab focus on mouse click or using"
" the arrows and the Tab keys on the keyboard. Use with :ref:`focus_mode "
"<class_Control_property_focus_mode>`."
msgstr ""
"**FOCUS_ALL** = **2** —— 该节点可以获取焦点，关于鼠标点击或使用键盘上的箭头和Tab键。与 "
":ref:`focus_mode <class_Control_property_focus_mode>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:384
msgid "enum **CursorShape**:"
msgstr "枚举 **CursorShape**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:386
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_ARROW** = **0** --- Show the system's arrow mouse cursor when "
"the user hovers the node. Use with :ref:`mouse_default_cursor_shape "
"<class_Control_property_mouse_default_cursor_shape>`."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_ARROW** = **0** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的箭头光标。与 "
":ref:`mouse_default_cursor_shape "
"<class_Control_property_mouse_default_cursor_shape>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:388
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_IBEAM** = **1** --- Show the system's I-beam mouse cursor when "
"the user hovers the node. The I-beam pointer has a shape similar to "
"\"I\". It tells the user they can highlight or insert text."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_IBEAM** = **1** —— 当用户悬停节点时，显示系统的I型光束鼠标光标。I型光束指针的形状类似于 "
"``I``。它告诉用户他们可以高亮或插入文本。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:390
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_POINTING_HAND** = **2** --- Show the system's pointing hand "
"mouse cursor when the user hovers the node."
msgstr "**CURSOR_POINTING_HAND** = **2** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的手形鼠标光标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:392
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_CROSS** = **3** --- Show the system's cross mouse cursor when "
"the user hovers the node."
msgstr "**CURSOR_CROSS** = **3** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的交叉鼠标光标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:394
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_WAIT** = **4** --- Show the system's wait mouse cursor, often an"
" hourglass, when the user hovers the node."
msgstr "**CURSOR_WAIT** = **4** —— 当用户悬停节点时，显示系统的等待鼠标光标，通常是一个沙漏。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:396
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_BUSY** = **5** --- Show the system's busy mouse cursor when the "
"user hovers the node. Often an hourglass."
msgstr "**CURSOR_BUSY** = **5** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的繁忙鼠标光标。通常是沙漏。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:398
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_DRAG** = **6** --- Show the system's drag mouse cursor, often a "
"closed fist or a cross symbol, when the user hovers the node. It tells "
"the user they're currently dragging an item, like a node in the Scene "
"dock."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_DRAG** = **6** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的拖动鼠标光标，通常是闭合的拳头或叉形符号。它告诉用户他们当前正在拖动项目，例如Scene码头中的节点。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:400
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_CAN_DROP** = **7** --- Show the system's drop mouse cursor when "
"the user hovers the node. It can be an open hand. It tells the user they "
"can drop an item they're currently grabbing, like a node in the Scene "
"dock."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_CAN_DROP** = **7** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的放下鼠标光标。它可以是张开的手。它告诉用户他们可以放下当前正在抓取的物品，例如Scene码头中的节点。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:402
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_FORBIDDEN** = **8** --- Show the system's forbidden mouse cursor"
" when the user hovers the node. Often a crossed circle."
msgstr "**CURSOR_FORBIDDEN** = **8** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统禁止的鼠标光标。通常是一个交叉的圆圈。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:404
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_VSIZE** = **9** --- Show the system's vertical resize mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. A double-headed vertical arrow. It "
"tells the user they can resize the window or the panel vertically."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_VSIZE** = **9** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的垂直调整大小的鼠标光标。双向垂直箭头。它告诉用户他们可以垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:406
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_HSIZE** = **10** --- Show the system's horizontal resize mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. A double-headed horizontal arrow. "
"It tells the user they can resize the window or the panel horizontally."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_HSIZE** = **10** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的水平调整大小的鼠标光标。双向水平箭头。它告诉用户他们可以水平调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:408
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE** = **11** --- Show the system's window resize mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. The cursor is a double-headed arrow"
" that goes from the bottom left to the top right. It tells the user they "
"can resize the window or the panel both horizontally and vertically."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE** = **11** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统窗口调整大小的鼠标光标。光标是从左下角到右上角的双向箭头。它告诉用户他们可以水平和垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:410
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_FDIAGSIZE** = **12** --- Show the system's window resize mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. The cursor is a double-headed arrow"
" that goes from the top left to the bottom right, the opposite of "
":ref:`CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE <class_Control_constant_CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE>`. It "
"tells the user they can resize the window or the panel both horizontally "
"and vertically."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_FDIAGSIZE** = **12** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统窗口调整大小的鼠标光标。光标是一个双箭头，从左上角到右下角，与 :ref:`CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE "
"<class_Control_constant_CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE>` 相反。它告诉用户他们可以水平和垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:412
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_MOVE** = **13** --- Show the system's move mouse cursor when the"
" user hovers the node. It shows 2 double-headed arrows at a 90 degree "
"angle. It tells the user they can move a UI element freely."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_MOVE** = **13** —— "
"当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的移动鼠标光标。它显示了两个成90度角的双箭头。它告诉用户他们可以自由移动UI元素。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:414
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_VSPLIT** = **14** --- Show the system's vertical split mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. On Windows, it's the same as "
":ref:`CURSOR_VSIZE <class_Control_constant_CURSOR_VSIZE>`."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_VSPLIT** = **14** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的垂直拆分鼠标光标。在Windows上，它与 "
":ref:`CURSOR_VSIZE <class_Control_constant_CURSOR_VSIZE>` 相同。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:416
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_HSPLIT** = **15** --- Show the system's horizontal split mouse "
"cursor when the user hovers the node. On Windows, it's the same as "
":ref:`CURSOR_HSIZE <class_Control_constant_CURSOR_HSIZE>`."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_HSPLIT** = **15** —— 当用户将节点悬停时，显示系统的水平拆分鼠标光标。在Windows上，它与 "
":ref:`CURSOR_HSIZE <class_Control_constant_CURSOR_HSIZE>` 相同。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:418
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_HELP** = **16** --- Show the system's help mouse cursor when the"
" user hovers the node, a question mark."
msgstr "**CURSOR_HELP** = **16** —— 当用户将节点悬停在节点上时，显示系统的帮助鼠标光标，一个问号。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:456
msgid "enum **LayoutPreset**:"
msgstr "枚举 **LayoutPreset**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:458
msgid ""
"**PRESET_TOP_LEFT** = **0** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the top-left of the"
" parent control's bounds. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_TOP_LEFT** = **0** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的左上角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:460
msgid ""
"**PRESET_TOP_RIGHT** = **1** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the top-right of "
"the parent control's bounds. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_TOP_RIGHT** = **1** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的右上角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:462
msgid ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_LEFT** = **2** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the bottom-left "
"of the parent control's bounds. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_LEFT** = **2** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的左下角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:464
msgid ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_RIGHT** = **3** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the bottom-"
"right of the parent control's bounds. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_RIGHT** = **3** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的右下角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:466
msgid ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_LEFT** = **4** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the center of "
"the left edge of the parent control's bounds. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_LEFT** = **4** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的左边缘的中心。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:468
msgid ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_TOP** = **5** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the center of the"
" top edge of the parent control's bounds. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_TOP** = **5** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的上边缘的中心。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:470
msgid ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_RIGHT** = **6** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the center of "
"the right edge of the parent control's bounds. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_RIGHT** = **6** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的右边缘的中心。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:472
msgid ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_BOTTOM** = **7** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the center of "
"the bottom edge of the parent control's bounds. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_CENTER_BOTTOM** = **7** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的下边缘的中心。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:474
msgid ""
"**PRESET_CENTER** = **8** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the center of the "
"parent control's bounds. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_CENTER** = **8** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件边界的右边缘的中心。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:476
msgid ""
"**PRESET_LEFT_WIDE** = **9** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the left edge of "
"the parent control. The left margin becomes relative to the left edge and"
" the top margin relative to the top left corner of the node's parent. Use"
" with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_LEFT_WIDE** = **9** —— "
"将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件的左边缘。左边距相对于节点父级的左边缘，而上边距相对于节点父节点的左上角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:478
msgid ""
"**PRESET_TOP_WIDE** = **10** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the top edge of "
"the parent control. The left margin becomes relative to the top left "
"corner, the top margin relative to the top edge, and the right margin "
"relative to the top right corner of the node's parent. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_TOP_WIDE** = **10** —— "
"将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件的上边缘。左边距相对于节点父级的左上角，上边距相对于节点父级的上边缘，而右边距相对于节点父节点的右上角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:480
msgid ""
"**PRESET_RIGHT_WIDE** = **11** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the right edge "
"of the parent control. The right margin becomes relative to the right "
"edge and the top margin relative to the top right corner of the node's "
"parent. Use with :ref:`set_anchors_preset "
"<class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_RIGHT_WIDE** = **11** —— "
"将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件的右边缘。右边距相对于节点父级的右边缘，而上边距相对于节点父节点的右上角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:482
msgid ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_WIDE** = **12** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the bottom edge"
" of the parent control. The left margin becomes relative to the bottom "
"left corner, the bottom margin relative to the bottom edge, and the right"
" margin relative to the bottom right corner of the node's parent. Use "
"with :ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_BOTTOM_WIDE** = **12** —— "
"将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件的下边缘。左边距相对于节点父级的左下角，而下边距相对于节点父节点的下边缘，而右边距相对于节点父节点的右下角。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:484
msgid ""
"**PRESET_VCENTER_WIDE** = **13** --- Snap all 4 anchors to a vertical "
"line that cuts the parent control in half. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_VCENTER_WIDE** = **13** —— 将所有4个锚点吸附到一条垂直线，该垂直线将父控件切成两半。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:486
msgid ""
"**PRESET_HCENTER_WIDE** = **14** --- Snap all 4 anchors to a horizontal "
"line that cuts the parent control in half. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_HCENTER_WIDE** = **14** —— 将所有4个锚点吸附到一条水平线，该水平线将父控件切成两半。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:488
msgid ""
"**PRESET_WIDE** = **15** --- Snap all 4 anchors to the respective corners"
" of the parent control. Set all 4 margins to 0 after you applied this "
"preset and the ``Control`` will fit its parent control. This is "
"equivalent to the \"Full Rect\" layout option in the editor. Use with "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**PRESET_WIDE** = **15** —— 将所有4个定位点吸附到父控件的各个角。应用此预设后，将所有4个边距设置为0，然后 "
"``Control`` 将填充其父控件。这等效于编辑器中的全角 ``Full Rect`` 布局选项。与 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>` 一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:502
msgid "enum **LayoutPresetMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **LayoutPresetMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:504
msgid ""
"**PRESET_MODE_MINSIZE** = **0** --- The control will be resized to its "
"minimum size."
msgstr "**PRESET_MODE_MINSIZE** = **0** —— 控件将被调整为其最小尺寸。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:506
msgid ""
"**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_WIDTH** = **1** --- The control's width will not "
"change."
msgstr "**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_WIDTH** = **1** —— 控件的宽度不会改变。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:508
msgid ""
"**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_HEIGHT** = **2** --- The control's height will not "
"change."
msgstr "**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_HEIGHT** = **2** —— 控件的高度不会改变。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:510
msgid "**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_SIZE** = **3** --- The control's size will not change."
msgstr "**PRESET_MODE_KEEP_SIZE** = **3** —— 控件的大小不会改变。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:526
msgid "enum **SizeFlags**:"
msgstr "枚举 **SizeFlags**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:528
msgid ""
"**SIZE_FILL** = **1** --- Tells the parent :ref:`Container "
"<class_Container>` to expand the bounds of this node to fill all the "
"available space without pushing any other node. Use with "
":ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` and "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>`."
msgstr ""
"**SIZE_FILL** = **1** —— 告诉父级 :ref:`Container <class_Container>` "
"扩展此节点的边界，以填充所有可用空间，而无需推动任何其他节点。与 :ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` 和 "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>` "
"一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:530
msgid ""
"**SIZE_EXPAND** = **2** --- Tells the parent :ref:`Container "
"<class_Container>` to let this node take all the available space on the "
"axis you flag. If multiple neighboring nodes are set to expand, they'll "
"share the space based on their stretch ratio. See "
":ref:`size_flags_stretch_ratio "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_stretch_ratio>`. Use with "
":ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` and "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>`."
msgstr ""
"**SIZE_EXPAND** = **2** —— 告诉父级 :ref:`Container <class_Container>` "
"让该节点，占用您标记的轴上的所有可用空间。如果将多个相邻节点设置为扩展，它们将根据其拉伸比共享空间。参见 "
":ref:`size_flags_stretch_ratio "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_stretch_ratio>`。与 "
":ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` 和 "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>` "
"一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:532
msgid ""
"**SIZE_EXPAND_FILL** = **3** --- Sets the node's size flags to both fill "
"and expand. See the 2 constants above for more information."
msgstr "**SIZE_EXPAND_FILL** = **3** —— 将节点的大小标志设置为同时填充和扩展。有关更多信息，请参见上面的2个常量。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:534
msgid ""
"**SIZE_SHRINK_CENTER** = **4** --- Tells the parent :ref:`Container "
"<class_Container>` to center the node in itself. It centers the control "
"based on its bounding box, so it doesn't work with the fill or expand "
"size flags. Use with :ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` and "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>`."
msgstr ""
"**SIZE_SHRINK_CENTER** = **4** —— 告诉父级 :ref:`Container <class_Container>`"
" 将节点在其中居中。它基于控件的边界框居中，因此它不适用于填充或扩展大小标志。与 :ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` 和 "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>` "
"一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:536
msgid ""
"**SIZE_SHRINK_END** = **8** --- Tells the parent :ref:`Container "
"<class_Container>` to align the node with its end, either the bottom or "
"the right edge. It doesn't work with the fill or expand size flags. Use "
"with :ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` and "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>`."
msgstr ""
"**SIZE_SHRINK_END** = **8** —— 告诉父级容器 :ref:`Container <class_Container>` "
"将节点与其末端（底部或右侧边缘）对齐。它不适用于填充或扩展大小标志。与 :ref:`size_flags_horizontal "
"<class_Control_property_size_flags_horizontal>` 和 "
":ref:`size_flags_vertical <class_Control_property_size_flags_vertical>` "
"一起使用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:548
msgid "enum **MouseFilter**:"
msgstr "枚举 **MouseFilter**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:550
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_STOP** = **0** --- The control will receive mouse button "
"input events through :ref:`_gui_input <class_Control_method__gui_input>` "
"if clicked on. And the control will receive the :ref:`mouse_entered "
"<class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` and :ref:`mouse_exited "
"<class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` signals. These events are "
"automatically marked as handled, and they will not propagate further to "
"other controls. This also results in blocking signals in other controls."
msgstr ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_STOP** = **0** —— 如果点击，控件将通过 :ref:`_gui_input "
"<class_Control_method__gui_input>` 接收鼠标按钮输入事件。并且控件将接收到 "
":ref:`mouse_entered <class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` 和 "
":ref:`mouse_exited <class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` "
"信号。这些事件会自动标记为已处理，并且不会进一步传播到其他控件。这也会导致其他控件中的信号阻塞。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:552
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_PASS** = **1** --- The control will receive mouse button "
"input events through :ref:`_gui_input <class_Control_method__gui_input>` "
"if clicked on. And the control will receive the :ref:`mouse_entered "
"<class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` and :ref:`mouse_exited "
"<class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` signals. If this control does not "
"handle the event, the parent control (if any) will be considered, and so "
"on until there is no more parent control to potentially handle it. This "
"also allows signals to fire in other controls. Even if no control handled"
" it at all, the event will still be handled automatically, so unhandled "
"input will not be fired."
msgstr ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_PASS** = **1** —— 如果点击，控件将通过 :ref:`_gui_input "
"<class_Control_method__gui_input>` 接收鼠标按钮输入事件。并且控件将接收到 "
":ref:`mouse_entered <class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` 和 "
":ref:`mouse_exited <class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` "
"信号。如果此控件不处理事件，则将考虑父控件（如果有），依此类推，直到不再有能够处理它的父控件为止。这也允许信号在其他控件中触发。即使完全没有控件处理该事件，该事件仍将自动处理，因此不会释放未处理的输入。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:554
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE** = **2** --- The control will not receive mouse "
"button input events through :ref:`_gui_input "
"<class_Control_method__gui_input>`. The control will also not receive the"
" :ref:`mouse_entered <class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` nor "
":ref:`mouse_exited <class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` signals. This "
"will not block other controls from receiving these events or firing the "
"signals. Ignored events will not be handled automatically."
msgstr ""
"**MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE** = **2** —— 控件将不会通过 :ref:`_gui_input "
"<class_Control_method__gui_input>` 接收鼠标按钮输入事件。控件也不会接收到 "
":ref:`mouse_entered <class_Control_signal_mouse_entered>` 和 "
":ref:`mouse_exited <class_Control_signal_mouse_exited>` "
"信号。这不会阻止其他控件接收这些事件或触发信号。忽略的事件将不会自动处理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:566
msgid "enum **GrowDirection**:"
msgstr "枚举 **GrowDirection**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:568
msgid ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_BEGIN** = **0** --- The control will grow to the left or"
" top to make up if its minimum size is changed to be greater than its "
"current size on the respective axis."
msgstr ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_BEGIN** = **0** —— "
"如果控件的最小尺寸更改为大于其各自轴上的当前尺寸，则控件将向左或顶部增大以进行补偿。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:570
msgid ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_END** = **1** --- The control will grow to the right or "
"bottom to make up if its minimum size is changed to be greater than its "
"current size on the respective axis."
msgstr ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_END** = **1** —— "
"如果控件的最小尺寸更改为大于其各自轴上的当前尺寸，则控件将向右或向下增大以进行补偿。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:572
msgid ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_BOTH** = **2** --- The control will grow in both "
"directions equally to make up if its minimum size is changed to be "
"greater than its current size."
msgstr ""
"**GROW_DIRECTION_BOTH** = **2** —— "
"如果控件的最小大小更改为大于其当前大小，则控件将在两个方向上均等地增长以补偿该控件。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:582
msgid "enum **Anchor**:"
msgstr "枚举 **Anchor**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:584
msgid ""
"**ANCHOR_BEGIN** = **0** --- Snaps one of the 4 anchor's sides to the "
"origin of the node's ``Rect``, in the top left. Use it with one of the "
"``anchor_*`` member variables, like :ref:`anchor_left "
"<class_Control_property_anchor_left>`. To change all 4 anchors at once, "
"use :ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**ANCHOR_BEGIN** = **0** —— 将4个锚点的一侧吸附到节点左上方的 ``Rect`` 的原点。与 ``anchor_*``"
" 成员变量之一，如 :ref:`anchor_left "
"<class_Control_property_anchor_left>`，一起使用。要一次更改所有4个锚点，使用 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:586
msgid ""
"**ANCHOR_END** = **1** --- Snaps one of the 4 anchor's sides to the end "
"of the node's ``Rect``, in the bottom right. Use it with one of the "
"``anchor_*`` member variables, like :ref:`anchor_left "
"<class_Control_property_anchor_left>`. To change all 4 anchors at once, "
"use :ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`."
msgstr ""
"**ANCHOR_END** = **1** —— 将4个锚点的一侧吸附到节点右下方的 ``Rect`` 的末端。与 ``anchor_*`` "
"成员变量之一，如 :ref:`anchor_left "
"<class_Control_property_anchor_left>`，一起使用。要一次更改所有4个锚点，使用 "
":ref:`set_anchors_preset <class_Control_method_set_anchors_preset>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:589
msgid "Constants"
msgstr "常量"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:609
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_RESIZED** = **40** --- Sent when the node changes size. "
"Use :ref:`rect_size <class_Control_property_rect_size>` to get the new "
"size."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_RESIZED** = **40** —— 当节点更改大小时发送。使用 :ref:`rect_size "
"<class_Control_property_rect_size>` 获取新的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:611
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_MOUSE_ENTER** = **41** --- Sent when the mouse pointer "
"enters the node."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_MOUSE_ENTER** = **41** —— 当鼠标指针进入节点时发送。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:613
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_MOUSE_EXIT** = **42** --- Sent when the mouse pointer "
"exits the node."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_MOUSE_EXIT** = **42** —— 当鼠标指针退出节点时发送。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:615
msgid "**NOTIFICATION_FOCUS_ENTER** = **43** --- Sent when the node grabs focus."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_FOCUS_ENTER** = **43** —— 当节点获得焦点时发送。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:617
msgid "**NOTIFICATION_FOCUS_EXIT** = **44** --- Sent when the node loses focus."
msgstr "**NOTIFICATION_FOCUS_EXIT** = **44** —— 当节点失去焦点时发送。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:619
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_THEME_CHANGED** = **45** --- Sent when the node's "
":ref:`theme <class_Control_property_theme>` changes, right before Godot "
"redraws the control. Happens when you call one of the ``add_*_override`` "
"methods."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_THEME_CHANGED** = **45** —— 当节点的 :ref:`theme "
"<class_Control_property_theme>` 更改时，就在Godot重绘控件之前，发送。当您调用 "
"``add_*_override`` 方法之一时发生。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:621
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_MODAL_CLOSE** = **46** --- Sent when an open modal dialog "
"closes. See :ref:`show_modal <class_Control_method_show_modal>`."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_MODAL_CLOSE** = **46** —— 当一个打开的模式对话框关闭时发送。参见 "
":ref:`show_modal <class_Control_method_show_modal>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:623
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_SCROLL_BEGIN** = **47** --- Sent when this node is inside "
"a :ref:`ScrollContainer <class_ScrollContainer>` which has begun being "
"scrolled."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_SCROLL_BEGIN** = **47** —— 当此节点在已开始滚动的 "
":ref:`ScrollContainer <class_ScrollContainer>` 中时发送。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:625
msgid ""
"**NOTIFICATION_SCROLL_END** = **48** --- Sent when this node is inside a "
":ref:`ScrollContainer <class_ScrollContainer>` which has stopped being "
"scrolled."
msgstr ""
"**NOTIFICATION_SCROLL_END** = **48** —— 当此节点在已停止滚动的 :ref:`ScrollContainer"
" <class_ScrollContainer>` 中时发送。"

