msgid ""
"Changes the tooltip text. The tooltip appears when the user's mouse "
"cursor stays idle over this control for a few moments, provided that the "
":ref:`mouse_filter <class_Control_property_mouse_filter>` property is not"
" :ref:`MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE <class_Control_constant_MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE>`."
" You can change the time required for the tooltip to appear with "
"``gui/timers/tooltip_delay_sec`` option in Project Settings."
msgstr ""
"更改工具提示文本。如果 :ref:`mouse_filter <class_Control_property_mouse_filter>` "
"属性不是 :ref:`MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE "
"<class_Control_constant_MOUSE_FILTER_IGNORE>` "
"属性，则用户的鼠标光标在此控件上闲置一会儿时，将显示工具提示。您可以使用项目设置中的 "
"``gui/timers/tooltip_delay_sec`` 选项，更改显示工具提示所需的时间。"

