#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:1190
msgid ""
"Virtual method to be implemented by the user. Returns a ``Control`` node "
"that should be used as a tooltip instead of the default one. Use "
"``for_text`` parameter to determine what text the tooltip should contain "
"(likely the contents of :ref:`hint_tooltip "
"<class_Control_property_hint_tooltip>`)."
msgstr ""
"用户要实现的虚拟方法。返回一个 ``Control`` 节点，该节点应用作一个工具提示，而不是默认提示。使用 ``for_text`` "
"参数确定工具提示应包含的文本（可能是 :ref:`hint_tooltip "
"<class_Control_property_hint_tooltip>` 的内容）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:1192
msgid ""
"The returned node must be of type ``Control`` or Control-derieved. It can"
" have child nodes of any type. It is freed when the tooltip disappears, "
"so make sure you always provide a new instance, not e.g. a node from "
"scene. When ``null`` or non-Control node is returned, the default tooltip"
" will be used instead."
msgstr ""
"返回的节点必须为 ``Control`` 类型或 ``Control`` "
"派生类型。它可以具有任何类型的子节点。当工具提示消失时，它将释放，因此请确保您始终提供一个新实例，而不是如场景中的节点。当返回 ``null`` "
"或非 ``Control`` 节点时，将使用默认工具提示代替。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:1194
msgid ""
"**Note:** The tooltip is shrunk to minimal size. If you want to ensure "
"it's fully visible, you might want to set its :ref:`rect_min_size "
"<class_Control_property_rect_min_size>` to some non-zero value."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：工具提示会缩小到最小尺寸。如果要确保它是完全可见的，则可能需要将其 :ref:`rect_min_size "
"<class_Control_property_rect_min_size>` 设置为一些非零值。"

