#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_control.rst:1650
msgid ""
"If ``push_opposite_anchor`` is ``true`` and the opposite anchor overlaps "
"this anchor, the opposite one will have its value overridden. For "
"example, when setting left anchor to 1 and the right anchor has value of "
"0.5, the right anchor will also get value of 1. If "
"``push_opposite_anchor`` was ``false``, the left anchor would get value "
"0.5."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``push_opposite_anchor`` 为 "
"``true``，并且相反的锚点与该锚点重叠，则相反的锚点其值将被覆盖。例如，当将左锚点设置为1，且右锚点的值为0.5时，右锚点的值也将为1。如果"
" ``push_opposite_anchor`` 为 ``false``，则左锚点的值将为0.5。"

